metadata.name: The Fool
metadata.description: The world is new and shiny to the Fool. Chances are taken, consequences a dim whisper. The cocktail of curiosity and immaturity is potent, and the lack of fear helps the world to shine brighter. The Fool is with you when there is: a beginning & end, inexperience, possibility, innocence, a new journey, purity of spirit, ignorance, immaturity, impulsiveness, recklessness, caution, subconscious connection to youth, playful innocence, exploration.
